title: Introducing the Levi's® 505™C
description:
Born in 1967, the 505™ jean came of age in the 70s New York punk scene. Pop artists, graffiti writers and rock stars all wore them, tore them and thrashed them. 

Now we introduce the 505™C, a modernized and remastered take on the ageless 505™ fit.
